WEBVTT

1
00:16:31.735 --> 00:16:36.667 
对我来说  洗鲸厂的工作  是最酷的工作
To me, working at the Wash was the coolest job in the ocean.

2
00:16:36.730 --> 00:16:38.701 
演示和说明

3
00:16:37.804 --> 00:16:41.891 
可是我学会一件永生难忘的事
But then I learned something I will never forget.

4
00:16:41.975 --> 00:16:44.373 
奥斯卡的爸爸是舌头洗刷工
Oscar's dad's a tongue scrubber!

5
00:16:44.446 --> 00:16:46.677 
舌头洗刷工  舌头洗刷员  舌头洗刷工
Tongue scrubber! Tongue scrubber!

6
00:16:52.715 --> 00:16:54.706 
我老爸是最棒的
My dad was the greatest.

7
00:16:54.779 --> 00:16:58.178 
可是没人喜欢无名小卒
But nobody loves a nobody.

8
00:16:59.691 --> 00:17:01.849 
我要为当大人物
I want to be a somebody.

